title: Episode 297: Fake Freak (Feat. Toosii)
itunes:title: Episode 297: Fake Freak (Feat. Toosii)
description:
Hip Hop artist, Toosii joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his upcoming single "Back Together." Toosii opens up about how he stole his girlfriend from her ex, getting over COVID, and much more. Toosii claims to be a freak in the sheets...but the ladies do everything in their power to prove otherwise. Enjoy!

Instrumentals produced by PERFXN and Big Len Music
